{"tid":2144144,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國引發三戰初期,美國又會好似一戰二戰咁,初期唔介入,後尾介入","createTime":"2020-08-07T13:46:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-17T06:36:30.000Z","uid":267658,"like":4,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"880ef14c3bf3063496cea5e243786181ca41aa01","tid":2144144,"uid":267658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T13:46:50.000Z","msg":"以目前的國際形勢和中美關係,中國好快就會引發三戰<br />\n<br />\n而美國和將來有機會做下位美國總統民主黨拜登的立場<br />\n我相信,又會好似一戰和二戰咁,爆發時和初期,都唔會介入戰爭<br />\n就算香港人被送哂入集中營、台灣和韓國被佔領,拜登都唔會介入戰爭<br />\n要等到被人攪,美國先至會介入三戰<br />\n<br />\n而咁啱,一戰和二戰爆發開始、初期、美國介入和結束戰爭<br />\n美國總統威爾遜、小羅斯福和杜魯門都係民主黨<br />\n<br />\n一戰就係齊默爾曼電報<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/c/ce/Ztel1b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fc%2Fce%2FZtel1b.jpg&h=3593b82d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/7/7e/Zimmermann-telegramm-offen.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2F7%2F7e%2FZimmermann-telegramm-offen.jpg&h=9409ce3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/DHn1Egt6Xdg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FDHn1Egt6Xdg&d=1Tw5YvH57m5vrKXwbFhC6PG%2BV2qV11Yco%2FuAlnZU2is%3D&h=d8d36c30\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/DHn1Egt6Xdg</a><br />\n<br />\n二戰就係珍珠港事件<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/jU3kvXOI5B8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FjU3kvXOI5B8&d=1Tw5YvH57m5vrKXwbFhC6PG%2BV2qV11Yco%2FuAlnZU2is%3D&h=62dd63ec\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/jU3kvXOI5B8</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/6lIm06JOBtw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F6lIm06JOBtw&d=1Tw5YvH57m5vrKXwbFhC6PG%2BV2qV11Yco%2FuAlnZU2is%3D&h=ebe1b064\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/6lIm06JOBtw</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/-Pmup_nTlXM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F-Pmup_nTlXM&d=1Tw5YvH57m5vrKXwbFhC6PG%2BV2qV11Yco%2FuAlnZU2is%3D&h=0c3cb77e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/-Pmup_nTlXM</a><br />\n<br />\n小羅斯福收到珍珠港被攻擊後的反應<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/4-L0AJOzl18\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F4-L0AJOzl18&d=1Tw5YvH57m5vrKXwbFhC6PG%2BV2qV11Yco%2FuAlnZU2is%3D&h=0a0867ff\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/4-L0AJOzl18</a><br />\n<br />\n小羅斯福在國會發表國恥演說<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/lK8gYGg0dkE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FlK8gYGg0dkE&d=1Tw5YvH57m5vrKXwbFhC6PG%2BV2qV11Yco%2FuAlnZU2is%3D&h=48de899d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/lK8gYGg0dkE</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/tPCkhybUB2s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FtPCkhybUB2s&d=1Tw5YvH57m5vrKXwbFhC6PG%2BV2qV11Yco%2FuAlnZU2is%3D&h=8c6df0e0\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/tPCkhybUB2s</a>"},{"pid":"c3c9379e8cc5cc5c3b7fc85e1f8d5b8bccf2386b","tid":2144144,"uid":345458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T13:47:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"66e09f64172c8a2648b38d07068405d5e182dd16","tid":2144144,"uid":267658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c3c9379e8cc5cc5c3b7fc85e1f8d5b8bccf2386b","tid":2144144,"uid":345458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T13:47:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T21:47:26.000Z","msg":"剛剛睇完<br />\n我只想講，有得走，就要快d走"},{"pid":"f94e14a3e0f617fd0808509ec3bc2f553c093426","tid":2144144,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T21:51:42.000Z","msg":"如果擺燈一開始就唔參戰好快俾人彈落台"},{"pid":"52d3fa86813f5c6919da3c99dfbaf2c704467f2e","tid":2144144,"uid":4396,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T21:57:54.000Z","msg":"傻啦，以而家呢個趨勢，拜登上到台再講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img sr